Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.05,0:13:19.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.59,0:13:22.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要哭  奈可奈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.98,0:13:25.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是被赋予面具之人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.37,0:13:28.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,面具使者的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.14,0:13:32.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不后悔
